  <name>NetPeek</name>
  <summary>Discover devices on your local network</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      NetPeek is a simple network scanner that helps you
      discover active devices on your local network. It shows open ports, hostnames,
      and allows easy rescan with a clean, user-friendly interface.
    </p>
  </description>
